The paper discusses the use of SDN techniques in the design of 5G wireless networks, which are primarily related to networking and communication (cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.COMM). The paper also discusses the challenges in this area, which could fall under the categories of architecture (cs.AR) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
